data.description: Stop the search! This is the one! We welcome you to this beautiful 4 bedroom, 3 baths well-established Home. Which offers a private inground Pool and Guest House. This home sits on 2.29 acres. When entering the doors, you are met with an amazing floor plan. The upgrades list goes on and on. The highlight upgrade is a brand-new deck, and brand new Hot Water Heater, the guest house has a brand-new AC unit, a septic system was pumped on 7/5/23, Exterior paint was done on both houses, and brand new light fixtures. The guest house has its own kitchen, living room, 2 bedrooms upstairs, 2 baths, and has its own septic system. Enjoy preparing meals in this extraordinary kitchen that’s equipped with plenty of counter and cabinet space to work with. It doesn’t end there!! Enjoy the large family room with the beautiful fireplace bringing enormous warmth and coziness to you and your guests. You can enjoy the sunroom all year round that overlooks the beautiful backyard and pool. All that is missing is you.
